public abstract class AbstractMiPController
extends AbstractController

Abstract AbstractMiController Class which provide convert data, operation, set message features.
This Class contains useful methods using 'MiPlatform' that is a software package of X-Internet.
If given parameter from client "isFR" is set "Y" or "y", response will be sent as firstrow. Firstrow is a way to send very big data from server to client. Send separated data with given parameter(nextDataSize). Firstrow only provides a way for Dataset object, not VariableList.

Author:
Jonghoon Kim, Youngmin Jo
